{{Infobox journal | title = Ancient Civilizations from Scythia to Siberia | cover = | editor = A. Ivantchik | discipline = History and archaeology | abbreviation = Anc. Civiliz. Scythia Sib. | publisher = [[Brill Publishers]] | country = | history = 1995-present | frequency = Bimonthly | website = http://www.brill.com/ancient-civilizations-scythia-siberia | link1 = | link1-name = | ISSN = 0929-077X | eISSN = 1570-0577 | JSTOR = | LCCN = | OCLC = }} '''''Ancient Civilizations from Scythia to Siberia''''' is a [[peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] the ancient and [[medieval history]] and archaeology of the former [[Soviet Union]]. The editor-in-chief is A. Ivantchik. The journal is published by [[Brill Publishers|Brill]] and indexed in [[Academic Search Complete]] and [[Scopus]].
