{{Italic title}} '''''Archaeologia Polona''''' is an [[academic journal]] of [[archaeology]] published in [[English language|English]] annually since 1958 by the Institute of Archaeology and Ethnology of the [[Polish Academy of Sciences]].<ref name="ArchPolona">{{cite web|url=http://www.iaepan.edu.pl/archaeologia-polona/|title=Archaeologia Polona, Journal of Archaeology|publisher=the Institute of Archaeology and Ethnology of the Polish Academy of Sciences|accessdate=2009-05-08}}</ref> The journal focuses on [[contemporary archaeology]] with particular respect to [[Poland]].
