'''''Waifs and Strays''''' is a short story collection by [[O. Henry]], released posthumously in 1917. It was published by [[Doubleday (publisher)|Doubleday, Page & Company]].<ref>{{cite book|authorlink=O. Henry|author=Henry, O.|date=1917|title=Waifs and Strays|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-YpIAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA223&lpg=PA223&dq=waifs+and+strays+o.+henry+new+york+times&source=bl&ots=5CfC6iw4BQ&sig=Eu1nAf6prKQcsHiafWvJeFifRXQ&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjE1LSzifjQAhVL8WMKHeRdCwM4ChDoAQgbMAE#v=onepage&q&f=false}}</ref>
